governess at the apartment in baabda east of beirut 
i am shocked by the horrific slayings hrawi was quoted by 
several beirut radio stations as saying thats a crime against 
the state aimed at sabotaging efforts to reunite the country and 
army after aouns ouster 
radios said hrawi made the comment in damascus where he is 
talking with syrian president hafez assad on how to enforce an arab 
leaguebrokered plan aimed at ending the civil war between moslems 
and christians 
we have declared that the peace process is open to all to join 
